column12:
'desc': [u'

Reid & Taylor Men's Checkered Formal Shirt Price: Rs.1441

Dress with style and perfection by wearing this blue and green checkered shirt from Reid and Taylor. This slim fit shirt with square cuffs and a round hem is crafted from cotton. The full sleeved shirt from Reid and Taylor is very comfortable that also makes you look smart
column13:
thereby enabling you to wear it to any formal occasion.

Enjoy your friend’s wedding by wearing this formal shirt from Reid and Taylor with a pair of formal trousers and oxford shoes of your choice. Complete your perfect formal look by adding a leather belt to your outfit. Reid and Taylor has been synonymous with consistently creating impeccable menswear and their line of formal shirts carry forward the brands legacy of marrying stringent quality with designs that spell out the refined taste of a fashion connoisseur.

Fabric Care

Gently machine wash this shirt in warm water and wash dark colours separately. Turn the shirt inside out while drying and washing. Avoid bleaching and do not wring. Tumble dry low and make sure not to soak the shirt for more than three hours. Use medium heat steam iron and do not iron on the prints.
